The closer I get to you, the worse it gets.
我越靠近你，情况就越糟。

296
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:42,600
The thought of not being with you, I mean, I just can't handle it.
想到不能和你在一起，我简直受不了。

297
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:45,280
We were made for each other, Veronica.
我们是天生一对，维罗妮卡。

298
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:48,240
You're my everything, my soulmate.
你是我的全部，我的灵魂伴侣。

299
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,920
What can I do?
我能做什么？

300
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:50,920
Just hold me.
只要抱着我就好。

301
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:53,920
I'll always be here for you, no matter what.
无论发生什么，我都会永远在你身边。

302
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:58,200
And together, we can tackle whatever life throws at us.
只要我们在一起，就能应对生活抛给我们的任何挑战。

303
